    <div id="description">
        <p>
            In this example, you can see how to render and configure text and image pointers in the linear gauge. The properties available in
            <a target="_blank" href="https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-js2/Syncfusion.EJ2.LinearGauge.LinearGaugePointer.html">e-lineargauge-pointer</a> and
            <a target="_blank" href="https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-js2/Syncfusion.EJ2.LinearGauge.LinearGaugeAnnotation.html">e-lineargauge-annotation</a> help in the customization of the text and image pointers in the linear gauge.
        </p>
        <p>
            More information on the pointers can be found in this
            <a target="_blank" href="https://ej2.syncfusion.com/aspnetcore/documentation/linear-gauge/pointers">documentation section</a>.
        </p>
    </div>
}
